action.suggestion: Please check routes definitions on MGW for interworking to CS Networks. Review ISUP / SIP-I and transcoding errors at media plane.

description.problemSignature: SIP - 500 Server Internal Error is found.
description.problemDescription: Cross domain root cause analysis of the  call  depicts the Request is rejected due to poor radio condition with UE lost.
description.posibleReason: Poor radio condition. Observed Sudden drop in radio condition. RSRP dropped from -93 to -115dBm in last 3 seconds before the call

action.suggestion: Please check  coverage issues and Radio conditions on cell PU0048A001.  Check tilts, coverage holes etc.

description.posibleReason: Resource Allocation failure due to PCC rule could not be successfully installed since the bearer eastablishment or modification procedure could not be completed successfully.

action.suggestion: Check PCEF (Policy and Charging Enforcement Function) at the Gateway (PGW). Fails to control over the user plane traffic handling at the Gateway and its QoS, service data flow detection and counting as well as online and offline charging interactions.

description.problemSignature: VoLTE Subscriber observed a call dropduring SRVCC process
description.problemDescription: VoLTE Subscriber went into poor LTE coverage in between the call.Subscriber tries to handover the call to WCDMA.Initiates SRVCC request, but get rejected from MSS.
description.posibleReason: Error in Codec Negotiation between MSS & ATCF.MSS rejects the Legacy Call leg by sending BYE message with Q.850 ; cause=47 .MSS reject the SRVCC request with cause ‘No resource Available’.

action.suggestion: Raise issue  to Vendor for RCA of the appearung cause on MSS. Check alarms, overload and resource availability issues.Issue reoccurred 17 times in past 1 week for the same cell.
